			</div>

			<div class="space-y-6">
				<div class="space-y-2 animate">
					<h3 class="font-medium">Trustscience</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">software engineer intern (nov 2022 - aug 2024 summers)</p>
					<p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
						built and enhanced financial integration workflows for client onboarding using Vue.js and AWS Lambda.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="space-y-2 animate">
